@startuml
!define RECTANGLE class

title Intrusion Detection System - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "Django URL Dispatcher" as URLDispatcher
participant "Authentication View" as AuthView
participant "User Model" as UserModel
participant "Dashboard View" as DashboardView
participant "File Upload Handler" as FileHandler
participant "ML Classifier\n(Random Forest)" as MLClassifier
participant "Scaler" as Scaler
participant "Result Model" as ResultModel
participant "History Model" as HistoryModel
participant "Recommendation Model" as RecommendationModel
participant "Template Engine" as TemplateEngine
database "SQLite Database" as DB

== User Registration ==
User -> Browser: Access signup page
Browser -> URLDispatcher: GET /signup
URLDispatcher -> AuthView: route to signup view
AuthView -> TemplateEngine: render signup template
TemplateEngine -> Browser: signup form
Browser -> User: display form

User -> Browser: submit registration data
Browser -> URLDispatcher: POST /signup
URLDispatcher -> AuthView: route to signup view
AuthView -> AuthView: validate form data
AuthView -> UserModel: create new user
UserModel -> DB: INSERT user record
DB -> UserModel: confirm creation
UserModel -> AuthView: user created
AuthView -> Browser: redirect to login
Browser -> User: show login page

== User Login ==
User -> Browser: enter credentials
Browser -> URLDispatcher: POST /login
URLDispatcher -> AuthView: route to login view
AuthView -> UserModel: authenticate user
UserModel -> DB: SELECT user by credentials
DB -> UserModel: user data
UserModel -> AuthView: authentication result
AuthView -> AuthView: create session
AuthView -> DB: store session data
AuthView -> Browser: redirect to dashboard
Browser -> User: show dashboard

== Traffic Analysis - File Upload ==
User -> Browser: access dashboard
Browser -> URLDispatcher: GET /dashboard
URLDispatcher -> DashboardView: route to dashboard view
DashboardView -> DashboardView: check authentication
DashboardView -> TemplateEngine: render dashboard template
TemplateEngine -> Browser: dashboard with upload form
Browser -> User: display upload interface

User -> Browser: select traffic capture file
Browser -> URLDispatcher: POST /dashboard/upload
URLDispatcher -> DashboardView: route to upload handler
DashboardView -> DashboardView: check authentication
DashboardView -> FileHandler: process uploaded file
FileHandler -> FileHandler: parse traffic data
FileHandler -> FileHandler: extract features

== Machine Learning Classification ==
FileHandler -> Scaler: scale feature values
Scaler -> Scaler: normalize data
Scaler -> FileHandler: scaled features
FileHandler -> MLClassifier: classify traffic data
MLClassifier -> MLClassifier: predict attack type
MLClassifier -> FileHandler: classification result

== Store Results ==
FileHandler -> ResultModel: create result record
ResultModel -> DB: INSERT detection result
DB -> ResultModel: confirm insert
ResultModel -> FileHandler: result saved

FileHandler -> RecommendationModel: get recommendation for attack
RecommendationModel -> DB: SELECT recommendation by attack type
DB -> RecommendationModel: recommendation data
RecommendationModel -> FileHandler: recommendation

FileHandler -> HistoryModel: create history entry
HistoryModel -> HistoryModel: associate with user (Foreign Key)
HistoryModel -> DB: INSERT history record
DB -> HistoryModel: confirm insert
HistoryModel -> FileHandler: history saved

== Display Results ==
FileHandler -> DashboardView: return analysis results
DashboardView -> TemplateEngine: render results template
TemplateEngine -> TemplateEngine: format attack type
TemplateEngine -> TemplateEngine: format recommendation
TemplateEngine -> Browser: results page
Browser -> User: display detection results

== View History ==
User -> Browser: request history
Browser -> URLDispatcher: GET /history
URLDispatcher -> DashboardView: route to history view
DashboardView -> DashboardView: check authentication
DashboardView -> HistoryModel: get user history
HistoryModel -> DB: SELECT history WHERE user_id
DB -> HistoryModel: history records
HistoryModel -> DashboardView: user history data
DashboardView -> TemplateEngine: render history template
TemplateEngine -> Browser: history page
Browser -> User: display past detections

== User Logout ==
User -> Browser: click logout
Browser -> URLDispatcher: POST /logout
URLDispatcher -> AuthView: route to logout view
AuthView -> AuthView: clear session
AuthView -> DB: delete session data
AuthView -> Browser: redirect to home
Browser -> User: show home page

@enduml
